glab-pipeline-wait - GitLab Pipeline Wait

USAGE:
    glab-pipeline-wait [--stage=stage-name]

DESCRIPTION:
    Wait for GitLab pipeline to complete. Monitors pipeline status
    and waits until terminal state is reached.

OPTIONS:
    --stage=stage-name
        Specific stage to wait for (required)

CONFIGURATION:
    -conf-dev-gitlab-pipeline-pipeline-name NAME
        Pipeline name to monitor

EXAMPLES:
    glab-pipeline-wait --stage=build
    glab-pipeline-wait --stage=test
